rComments: He is always willing to help students. He answers our questions, always willing to help after class. assignments are easy if you study and attend the class. 302 is not easy, but if you take him, you would have no problems.

He really goes out of his way to help you. It is his first year actually teaching so he is still figuring things out but he really does want to help you and make sure you understand what you are doing. He is super nice and tries to make things as fair as possible.
